name: editABankAccount

testSteps.description: Given that im logged into manage bank account page

children.description: When i open page from sidebar menu: {Supplier Management,Manage Bank Account}

exception.message: Expected condition failed: waiting for visibility of element located by By.xpath: //div[@class = 'sidebar-menu-container'] (tried for 10 second(s) with 100 milliseconds interval)

testSteps.description: Then the manage bank account page and its contents should show up
When I set the 'Supplier' to '54556'
When i click search button
Then a search result should show up
Then the bank account number of the first supplier bank account should have a value
When i click on edit button of the first supplier bank account
Then the add bank account form should show up
Then the internal information accordion form should be opened
When I set the 'GL Banck Account' to '1LON400.41EUR0'
When i click accordion continue button
Then the beneficiary bank accordion form should be opened
When I set the 'Swift Code' to 'AUBKPHMM'
When i click on validate button
When I set the 'Bank Name' to 'Edited Bank Account Test Name'
When I set the 'Customer Bank Account' to '9334410498'
When I set the 'Bank Address' to 'Makati'
When I set the 'City' to 'Makati'
When I set the 'Country' to 'Philippines'
When i click accordion continue button
Then the payment instructions accordion form should be opened
When i click save button
Then the bank account edited successfully notification should show up

title: Edit a bank account
